  Lines:
  - Oh you're back. Let's start the ritual then.
  - '*magic chants*'
  - Uh... When I said I unlocked the third eye, I didn't mean it literally...
  - Well you seem fine though. You can use magic now!
  - Also, I think Wingus is looking for you. You should come back to him.
